---

<section class="home-stats-overlap relative z-20 px-4 pb-4 font-body">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto stats-bar-shell">
    <div class="stats-bar-item">
      <div class="stats-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg class="w-7 h-7" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 14l9-5-9-5-9 5 9 5z"/>
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 14l6.16-3.422a12.083 12.083 0 01.665 6.479A11.952 11.952 0 0012 20.055a11.952 11.952 0 00-6.824 2.998 12.078 12.078 0 01.665-6.479L12 14z"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-display text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-1">
          <span class="home-ssr-et">Üle 10 aasta praktikat</span>
          <span class="home-ssr-ru">Свыше 10 лет практики</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="text-white/90 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          <span class="home-ssr-et">Toruabi, kanalisatsioon ja boiler — sertifitseeritud meistrid.</span>
          <span class="home-ssr-ru">Торуаби, канализация и бойлер — сертифицированные мастера.</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="stats-bar-item">
      <div class="stats-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg class="w-7 h-7" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-display text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-1">
          <span class="home-ssr-et">5000+ sooritatud tellimust</span>
          <span class="home-ssr-ru">5000+ выполненных заказов</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="text-white/90 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          <span class="home-ssr-et">Selge hind enne tööd ja korralik lõpptulemus.</span>
          <span class="home-ssr-ru">Понятная цена до работ и аккуратный результат.</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="stats-bar-item">
      <div class="stats-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg class="w-7 h-7" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-display text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-1">
          <span class="home-ssr-et">Kiire väljakutse 24/7</span>
          <span class="home-ssr-ru">Срочный выезд 24/7</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="text-white/90 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          <span class="home-ssr-et">Tavaliselt kohal 30–60 min jooksul Tallinnas ja Harjumaal.</span>
          <span class="home-ssr-ru">Обычно на месте за 30–60 минут в Таллине и Харьюмаа.</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
